snippet: Emeli Sandé, whose debut album is “Our Version of Events,” has many influences but a distinct sound of her own.
abstract: Jon Caramanica assesses the debut album by British soul singer Emeli Sande, who draws from diverse musical styles to create her own distinct sound.
lead_paragraph: Emeli Sandé, whose debut album is “Our Version of Events,” has many influences but a distinct sound of her own.

headline.main: A Singer With Many Influences but a Soul That’s Hers Alone
